                        ay to install the theme is to fork it using GitHub.
                        Check the README ay to install the theme is to fork it
                        using GitHub. Check the READMEay to install the theme
                      </p>

                      <div class="flex justify-between">
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex items-center">
                          <span class="icon h-4 w-4 mr-1 flex items-center ">
                            <svg
                              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                              fill="none"
                              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                              stroke-width="1.5"
                              stroke="currentColor"
                              class="w-6 h-6"
                            >
